name: cadmv
tagline: Check the first available appointment date for a CA DMV office
body:
### Welcome to cadmv GitHub Pages.
I just want to easily get the first available appointment date, and trying GitHub Pages.

```
$ git clone https://github.com/williamchai/cadmv.git
$ cd cadmv
$ python cadmv.py
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
